/i>. <a href=\"/ICGA_Journal#38_4\" title=\"ICGA Journal\">ICGA Journal, Vol. 38, No. 4</a>&#160;» <a href=\"/18th_Computer_Olympiad#Draughts\" title=\"18th Computer Olympiad\">18th Computer Olympiad | Draughts</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Jan-Jaap_van_Horssen\" title=\"Jan-Jaap van Horssen\">Jan-Jaap van Horssen</a> (<b>2018</b>). <i>Complexity of checkers and draughts on different board sizes</i>. <a href=\"/ICGA_Journal#40_4\" title=\"ICGA Journal\">ICGA Journal, Vol. 40, No. 4</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Draughts&amp;action=edit&amp;section=13\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2010_..._2\">2010 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Draughts&amp;action=edit&amp;section=14\" title=\"Edit section: 2010 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://laatste.info/bb3/viewtopic.php?t=3819\">(Free) draughts software</a> by A. Presman, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://laatste.info/bb3/index.php\">World Draughts Forum</a>, April 21, 2012</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=56170\">Draughts at the ICGA Olympiad</a> by <a href=\"/Harm_Geert_Muller\" title=\"Harm Geert Muller\">Harm Geert Muller</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 30, 2015</li></ul>\n<dl><dd> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=56170&amp;start=2\">Re: Draughts at the ICGA Olympiad</a> by <a href=\"/Fabien_Letouzey\" title=\"Fabien Letouzey\">Fabien Letouzey</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, Ap